document_data.History:
Aksa was born in {{YearlinkConvert|1670|NY}}. The fierce arcanist experimented with several types of spells throughout his life. He created his first spell, ''[[mending]]'', at only 21 years old in {{YearlinkConvert|1691|NY}}. When he developed his ''[[disintegrate]]'' spell and tested it in his home, he expected it to remove an entire wall, but bored a number of one-inch holes instead. Utterly fascinated by the odd behaviour of the spell, he cast it twice more and unintentionally caused the entire northern face of his house to collapse from the structural damage. Aka was unruffled by the minor disaster and simply set about altering the spell and testing it on the southern side of his house while builders worked to repair what he had destroyed. In {{YearlinkConvert|1840|NY}}, the Destroyer finally met his end.

In his time, Aksa developed the following spells:
* [[Aksa's repair]], in {{YearlinkConvert|1691|NY}}
* [[Aksa's object]], in {{YearlinkConvert|1718|NY}}
* [[Aksa's growth]], in {{YearlinkConvert|1724|NY}}
* [[Aksa's contrivance]], in {{YearlinkConvert|1728|NY}}
* [[Aksa's shatter]], in {{YearlinkConvert|1728|NY}}
* [[Aksa's disintegrate]], in {{YearlinkConvert|1764|NY}}
* [[Aksa's glassteel]], in {{YearlinkConvert|1766|NY}}
* [[Aksa's passage]], in {{YearlinkConvert|1801|NY}}
* [[Aksa's morphing]], in {{YearlinkConvert|1820|NY}}
